<h1><span style="color: #ffffff;">Health</span></h1>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><em>"When we took over, our hospitals were in a sorry state. They lacked common drugs. No government can neglect the health of its people and expect to make a worthwhile progress."</em></p>
